tion
with you when they have a matter that they wish to discuss. These messages =
from
other empires will show up at the top-right of your screen &#8211; click on=
 the
message to open communications and respond to the other empire.<o:p></o:p><=
/span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>There are a number of
